2026-05-18T06:16:04.4835696Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-18T06:16:04.4836383Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-18T06:16:04.4837103Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-18T06:16:04.4837937Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-18T06:16:04.4838721Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-18T06:16:04.4839506Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
