2026-05-18T06:16:04.9569524Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-18T06:16:04.9569797Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-18T06:16:04.9570101Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-18T06:16:04.9570392Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-18T06:16:04.9570680Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-18T06:16:04.9571138Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
